title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Mixture control
description:
In this how to we are going to look at how to use the mixture control functionality from an aircraft. After a small piece of explanation we will go airborne to see what the effect is using the mixture control during a flight. In addition I will show you how to set the mixture control to automatic if you don't want to control it manually.
